Whoever wishes to know the method of compounding chin i huan tan (gold
fluid returned medicine) ought to begin by seeding and planting it in
his own garden. It is needless to borrow the help of blowing or
fanning (the fire)ï¼š the tan will ripen naturally and emerge from the
true womb.
